parameters:
General Atu: Regardless of their individual strength, their
numbers are troublesome. The soldiers have been quite
exhausted from the daily battles.

General Atu: Honestly... Where were they hiding in the
Empire?

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: It's because you guys are
slacking off that they keep appearing!
Storge of Love: Is this the time to be fighting!?

Storge of Love: They're coming towards the airship! This is
bad, someone, head towards the airship!
Clea: Sorry to keep you waiting. Leave the airship to us!

Clea: This airship is the lifeline of our operation. We
will definitely protect it to reach the dragons.

Clea: We were able to protect the airship, but... this
number is...!
General Atu: A new tactic at this timing...

General Atu: We will retreat to the planned location!
Abandon the garrison! Rest assured, my and Shimosu's units
will hold the rear, so fall back!
Clea: What are we going to do about the airship!?

General Atu: You should understand, right? To deal with
this number of enemies, we have no choice but to regroup!

Clea: The crystal of the airship is extremely valuable! And
we don't know how long the dragons will stay here!

Clea: We can't let the dragons do as they please! If we
leave them alone, it will give birth to a different version
of myself!

General Atu: They have started moving...! Our conversation
ends here with you.
Shimosu of the Unknown Night: What's this, a new tactic!?

Storge of Benevolence: L-Look! The goblin's advance has
stopped!?
Storge of Benevolence: What on earth is happening...?
Clea: Thank goodness... You made it in time!
Voice Priestess Phoni: I apologize for the wait, Clea-san.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Next, I will assist you. I won't let
anyone interfere with your wish!

Voice Priestess Phoni: Forces of darkness... leave this
place at once!
Storge of Benevolence: Wow... the enemy is retreating.

General Atu: The tide has turned! Push back the enemy all
at once! Full force! Follow my lead!

Researcher Caron: It seems like the preparations for the
airship are coming along somehow. It's a bit insensitive,
but thinking about the large-scale experiment gets me
excited.

Researcher Caron: By the way, how did you manage to
convince the Archmage?

Researcher Caron: Perhaps my recommendation played a role
in it!

Mage Relm: D-Dokusa-san!? Why are you here in a place like
this!

Researcher Dokusa: It's partly because of his help... but
I'm also curious about Assistant Candidate No. 3 and his
companions!

Researcher Dokusa: A ridiculous and grand purpose...! As a
researcher, it makes me want to support it.
Clea: Thank you very much, everyone.

Researcher Caron: Now, let's resume the test. We need to
fly the unmanned airship...

Researcher Caron: Controlling the crystal, ensuring the
minimum flight distance... We absolutely cannot afford to
fail. Let's prepare until the very last moment.

One-armed Opro: 'I managed to make it in time for the
decisive battle after defeating the goblins along the way.
I'm glad.'
One-armed Opro: 'Well... How many can I kill today?'

Explorer Armada: It's quite lively, isn't it? I'll do my
best not to be a burden.
Explorer Armada: Phew... Women have courage!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: The tension is making my skin
crawl... This battlefield seems tailor-made for the Bulk
Gang!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Brave warriors! Witness the battle
prowess of this goat!

Cors the Wanderer: Sigh, I've ended up in quite an out-of-
place location...

Cors the Wanderer: I have various things I want to ask, so
please don't die, okay?

Researcher Caron: It will take a little time until launch.
If the airship experiences a significant impact, it might
fail.

Researcher Caron: No matter what happens, please make sure
to defend it to the death!

General Atu: Understood! We will now commence the operation
to subdue the dragon!

General Atu: This operation is a recreation of a myth! We
will surely succeed and become the reincarnation of heroes!

Imperial Soldier: The enemy has begun their advance! It's
the largest number we've ever seen!

Voice Priestess Phoni: Leave it to me! I will create a path
for Clea and the others!

General Atu: The enemy's movements have slowed down! Let's
kick those goblins who came ahead of us!
General Atu: Caron! Prepare for levitation!

Researcher Caron: Understood! We have 100% remaining until
levitation preparation is complete...!

Researcher Caron: Only 30% remaining until levitation
preparation is complete...!
Researcher Caron: It's safe to move to Mount Monimos!

Voice Priestess Phoni: I-I'm fine...! I will create a path
for Clea and the others...!

Voice Priestess Phoni: As long as my magic is affecting it,
I won't let anyone interfere with Clea and the others.
Voice Priestess Phoni: Please go! Please trust me!
Clea: I'm going... I will definitely come back!
別ページに分けて、すり抜けONにしないと、
イベントのところで引っかかるため、2ページに分けている

Researcher Caros: I swear on the pride of the Academy that
we will prepare until the very last moment.
別ページに分けて、すり抜けONにしないと、
イベントのところで引っかかるため、2ページに分けている

Researcher Dokusa: Let's challenge the threats of the world
together, shall we?
別ページに分けて、すり抜けONにしないと、
イベントのところで引っかかるため、2ページに分けている

Celis, the Gale: Clea... Shall we have a chat, just the two
of us after a long time?
Celis, the Gale: That's right, before I forget... this.

Celis, the Gale: I received this from Kurumi Piste-san,
who has the ability to enhance powers.

Celis, the Gale: I can cultivate and increase it a little.
I want Clea to decide whether to receive it now or not.

Celis, the Gale: Alright, I understand. I want you to
accept it.

Celis, the Gale: I feel a little relieved... because you're
thinking about what will happen after the dragon.

Celis, the Gale: I'll bury it in the courtyard of the
Adventurer Guild's dormitory. Harvest it after the dragon's
subjugation is over, okay?
